; H7.5 Free names and same-spelling binders are distinct after mrho elaboration.
; The received payload contains a free $x. Substitution descends under an
; inner input binder also spelled $x, but the elaborator has already given that
; binder a distinct identity, so the free name remains free.
(rho:par
  (rho:recv (rho:quote rho:nil) $y
    (rho:recv (rho:quote rho:nil) $x
      (rho:drop $y)))
  (rho:send (rho:quote rho:nil) (rho:drop $x)))
